name: v3.0.0
body:
### Support Swift 3.0
- `id` is now mapped to `Any`
  
  [[SE-0116] Import Objective-C id as Swift Any type](https://github.com/apple/swift-evolution/blob/master/proposals/0116-id-as-any.md)
- OptionSetType => OptionSet
- ErrorType => ErrorProtocol => Error
- AuthenticationPolicy to be UInt
- Drop `NS` prefix
  - NSData => Data
  - NSURL => URL
  - NSIndexSet => IndexSet
- Lowercase enums (adn OptionSet types)

### Update to Xcode 8 recommended build settings
- Enable whole module optimization (by default on Xcode 8)

### Bug fixes
- [x] Enable to catch specific errors

name: v1.2.1
body:
Now available set/get NSData to keychain by subscripting.

``` swift
let data = keychain[data:"JSONData"]
keychain[data: "JSONData"] = JSONData
```
First release
Support Swift 1.2
Support Shared Web Credentials (iOS 8+)
Support TouchID and Keychain integration (iOS 8+)
